  <description>The Do Not Touch button is more than ever an immersive experience by bringing the wild world of Nickelodeon right into your living room! 
  Keep pushing the button, every time something unexpected happen. 
  Help SpongeBob to catch jellyfishes, become an artist by painting all over your space or just discover hidden messages when you switch off the light!</description>

